(firstQuint)Prevalence of Genital HPV Infection in Males Following Introduction of Universal Male HPV Vaccination.

 Males aged 17 to 19 in Australia will be recruited from 2014.

 Men will undergo sampling from the penis for HPV.

 The prevalence of HPV infection will be determined in 2014-2015 and compared to the prevalence in 2016-2017.

.

